commit c58679bf00a72fe744b1467610ad735d62c0886d
Author: Tristan Van Berkom <tristan.van.berkom@gmail.com>
Date:   Sat Jan 7 15:55:43 2012 +0900

    widget: Handle NULL ClutterEventCrossing->related actor in mx_widget_leave
    
    In the case that the mouse exits the stage, the ->related actor
    argument will be NULL, this needs to be caught before sending
    the NULL actor to clutter_actor_contains() and firing a needless
    assertion failure.

 mx/mx-widget.c | 3 ++-
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

