commit 192ac9ea0a52c2e4d505c116805c06dca834f367
Author: Thomas Wood <thomas.wood@intel.com>
Date:   Mon Oct 10 17:45:51 2011 +0100

    scroll-bar: set the parent of the handle to the scroll bar itself
    
    The scroll bar is responsible for allocating and painting the handle,
    therefore, the handle's parent must be set to the scroll bar.

 mx/mx-scroll-bar.c | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

commit 7646a3e071a5c16a9deb445e2392cb1b62eaf4e1
Author: Thomas Wood <thomas.wood@intel.com>
Date:   Mon Oct 10 10:50:43 2011 +0100

    action: use g_object_class_override_property to add the GAction properties
    
    Using g_object_class_override_property prevents duplication of property
    metadata and ensures the properties are compatible with the interface.
    
    The GAction property definitions also changed between glib 2.28 and 2.30
    and are now read only, so this commit prevents the GAction properties from
    being writable using g_object_set_property.

 mx/mx-action.c | 103 ++++++++++++---------------------------------------------
 1 file changed, 21 insertions(+), 82 deletions(-)

