commit fa25ce86adc8894945d9cd5522c1df877b886ae2
Author: Thomas Wood <thomas.wood@intel.com>
Date:   Tue Sep 27 14:34:36 2011 +0100

    image/texture-cache: adjust pointer types for changes in Cogl API

