commit 49e075f879d928c3e95e3c029a4d666e0e2d9a0d
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Fri Jun 3 15:29:02 2011 +0100

    Release 1.2.0

 NEWS         | 25 +++++++++++++++++++++++++
 configure.ac |  4 ++--
 2 files changed, 27 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

commit a4f396cf441a516e8cdd4778543184e39f9167c0
Author: Neil Roberts <neil@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Tue May 31 14:56:56 2011 +0100

    mx-offscreen: Handle redirecting a ClutterStage specially
    
    When redirecting a ClutterStage there's no need to calculate our own
    modelview matrix because the one for the stage will already be set up
    render to a buffer of the same size. This gives the best chance of
    rendering exactly the same geometry as would be rendered to the stage
    even if Clutter changes how it calculates its modelview matrix. This
    is important when the offscreen is used to temporarily apply an effect
    to the stage such as from MxDialog.
    
    This also makes it avoid calling cogl_clear for stages because the
    paint implementation for the stage also does a clear so it's a
    waste. Having the clear there also allows Mx to take advantage of
    Clutter's optimisation to avoid clearing when the
    CLUTTER_STAGE_NO_CLEAR_ON_PAINT hint is set.
    
    http://bugzilla.clutter-project.org/show_bug.cgi?id=2658

 mx/mx-offscreen.c | 44 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-------------
 1 file changed, 31 insertions(+), 13 deletions(-)

commit 0ef932a2c8c64969be0418ba424fc8f8c796549c
Author: Neil Roberts <neil@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Thu May 26 15:13:59 2011 +0100

    mx-offscreen: Always use an aspect ratio of 1.0 for the perspective
    
    The code for calculating modelview matrix no longer works since
    Clutter changed the aspect ratio for its perspective matrix. This
    patch changes it to override the aspect ratio back to 1.0 so that it
    will continue to work.
    
    http://bugzilla.clutter-project.org/show_bug.cgi?id=2658

 mx/mx-offscreen.c | 12 ++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 12 insertions(+)

commit e5a8cfa6360e4e7a37da141a6235dc2aa233a6a1
Author: Raul Gutierrez Segales <raul.gutierrez.segales@collabora.co.uk>
Date:   Fri May 13 17:33:54 2011 +0000

