commit 8d93f02b33f6d9a6a151d9847b29479e36d26553
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Thu May 19 10:39:21 2011 +0100

    icon-theme: Allow reliable overriding of the system icon theme
    
    When mx_icon_theme_set_theme_name() is called, this will permanently
    override the system icon theme setting. The icon theme can be reset to the
    system setting by calling this function with a NULL theme name.

 mx/mx-icon-theme.c | 32 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++--
 1 file changed, 30 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

