commit 037e564e6d0a8b79bc3205f0935e0bd9f0411049
Author: Thomas Wood <thomas.wood@intel.com>
Date:   Wed Apr 27 11:07:12 2011 +0100

    bin: clarify the documentation for mx_bin_allocate_child
    
    The "box" parameter is expected to be the parent's allocation and since the
    allocation of the child is always relative to its parent, only the width
    and height of the box is used.

