commit a7d3bf7376d4cb3713faf166f5d42f211e094c63
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Wed Apr 6 20:15:41 2011 +0100

    actor-manager: Add mx_actor_manager_cancel_operations
    
    Add a new function, mx_actor_manager_cancel_operations, that will cancel
    all operations associated with a particular actor. Use this new function
    in the remove_container function to cancel operations relating to the
    container before removing it.

