commit 4f5f024d986140221c0781e9617dca2c6baad754
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Wed Mar 30 19:29:17 2011 +0100

    texture-cache: Fix adding an item to the cache twice
    
    If you load an image from the cache that has only previously had meta-data
    attached to it, it will end up being added to the cache hash-table again.

