commit 4eb89dc202c83520cf373cb0de08c881940acb9d
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Wed Mar 30 18:50:08 2011 +0100

    image: Refinements, documentation and bug-fixes
    
    There was a lost commit(s) and MxImage ended up in a somewhat inconsistent
    state. Go over it, fix some of the left errors and document the internals
    a bit more comprehensively.
    
    In particular, if image load fails, the error should always be set now,
    and cached image use shouldn't have any glitches. Hopefully.

 mx/mx-image.c | 208 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++----------------
