Date:   Wed Mar 16 10:29:50 2011 +0000

    texture-cache: Add a destroy notify for cache items
    
    Add mx_texture_cache_item_free() as the destroy function for cached items.
    Related, correct the pointer type in the item struct and make sure to
    unref the item pointer in the free function.

 mx/mx-texture-cache.c | 12 +++++++-----
 1 file changed, 7 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)

commit 3e574a05b9b4164dd0c080059d8a9da6a71bf9db
