 mx/mx-texture-cache.c                | 85 +++++++++++++++++++++++++-----------
 mx/mx-texture-cache.h                |  3 ++
 3 files changed, 63 insertions(+), 26 deletions(-)

commit ae8a111f1fd93b656a0210d9908fb7654d91ac51
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Wed Mar 16 10:03:02 2011 +0000

    texture-cache: Update to handle URIs as well as paths
    
    Handle URIs as well as paths, and store entries in the cache with their
    URI as the key instead of the filename. This will allow us to later extend
    MxTextureCache to hold arbitrary URIs instead of just local files.

 mx/mx-texture-cache.c | 144 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++---------
 mx/mx-texture-cache.h |   8 +--
 2 files changed, 122 insertions(+), 30 deletions(-)

commit e655dcb8a1f37529ea2cd329a1b5bb4d41703e26
Author: Jussi Kukkonen <jku@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Tue Mar 22 14:48:32 2011 +0200

    focus-manager: handle focus when focused actor is unparented
    
    Currently we lose focus when an actor is e.g. destroyed.
    This commit pushes focus to old parent when the focused widget
    is unparented.
    
    Also adds a small test case.

 mx/mx-focus-manager.c | 85 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++------
 tests/Makefile.am     |  2 ++
 tests/test-focus.c    | 76 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 3 files changed, 153 insertions(+), 10 deletions(-)

