commit 2eb30a8501aaf5767a5c1398b8370e1516465652
Author: Thomas Wood <thomas.wood@intel.com>
Date:   Tue Feb 22 14:50:54 2011 +0000

    scroll-view: connect to actor-added and actor-removed signals
    
    Use the actor-added and actor-removed signals rather than overriding the
    actor_add and actor_remove virtual functions to get notifications about
    when an actor is added or removed from the container. This allows
    mx_bin_set_child to work as expected when applied to an MxScrollView.
    
    http://bugzilla.clutter-project.org/show_bug.cgi?id=2281

 mx/mx-scroll-view.c | 27 +++++++--------------------
 1 file changed, 7 insertions(+), 20 deletions(-)

