commit e5ad8e1f0b571965b5db85f4a43c7470deb7ed54
Author: Thomas Wood <thomas.wood@intel.com>
Date:   Mon Feb 7 16:37:39 2011 +0000

    stack: add a 'fit' child property
    
    The 'fit' child property attempts to fit the actor into the available space
    while respecting the actor's width-for-height or height-for-width
    constraints.

