commit 53a76c7f78e98520b1c905eb22d0f0a312a4fe51
Author: Rob Bradford <rob@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Mon Feb 7 16:51:31 2011 +0000

    build: Fix embarrassing copy and paste error in previous bug fix

 configure.ac | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

commit 182ee7b726d595e4e2ae536b41798fe2ec705e15
Author: Rob Bradford <rob@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Mon Feb 7 12:23:39 2011 +0000

    build: Fix behaviour of --disable-gtk-widgets
    
    This was caused by a mistake in the use of AC_ARG_ENABLE. The first parameter
    is used when the option is used in any form, either --enable or --disable. In
    this case the bug was that when any mode was used the enable value was
    overriden to no meaning that --enable-gtk-widgets would actually disable gtk
    widget building.
    
    The correct solution here was to set the default value in the second case of
    AC_ARG_ENABLE (not specified) and then use the actual enable value to decide
    whether to enable or not.
    
    Fixes: http://bugzilla.clutter-project.org/show_bug.cgi?id=2552

 configure.ac | 15 +++++++++++----
 1 file changed, 11 insertions(+), 4 deletions(-)

commit 8aa48747cd239cb353d6e7b2b7fd04ebbad793d3
Author: Robert Ancell <robert.ancell@gmail.com>
Date:   Mon Feb 7 12:16:57 2011 +0000

    build: Fix DSO link issues
    
    Let's make sure all the symbols are defined at link time. The Fedora
    project tries to ensure that distribution wide. For more details See:
    http://fedoraproject.org/w/index.php?title=UnderstandingDSOLinkChange
    
    Fixes: http://bugzilla.clutter-project.org/show_bug.cgi?id=2523

 tests/Makefile.am | 4 ++--
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

commit abf9ba363fbfe94c618df477d1277c8faa6d5adb
