commit c99c487ba6ddf87d81ddd915a75e3eca63a30b88
Author: Neil Roberts <neil@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Fri Jan 28 12:28:16 2011 +0000

    mx-window-x11: Use ARGB to get the texture data on big endian
    
    The _NET_WM_ICON property expects the alpha component to be in the
    most significant byte and the blue component to be in the least
    significant byte which means that on a big endian architecture the
    data format retrieved from Cogl would need to be in the reverse order.
    
    http://bugzilla.clutter-project.org/show_bug.cgi?id=2533

 mx/x11/mx-window-x11.c | 15 +++++++++++++--
 1 file changed, 13 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

commit 289887513639aa8a77fa9695bcf116b15b3732bb
Author: Neil Roberts <neil@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Thu Jan 27 13:36:59 2011 +0000

    mx-window-x11: Fix mx_window_x11_set_wm_hints for 64-bit archs
    
    For some reason XChangeProperty always takes an array of longs when
    the format is 32 even on architectures where sizeof(long) != 32. The
    RGBA data we get from Cogl is packed into 32-bit values so on 64-bit
    architectures we need to expand these values to longs. This was
    causing a crash when using a custom icon on 64-bit because libX11
    would try to read past the end of the data array.
    
    http://bugzilla.clutter-project.org/show_bug.cgi?id=2533

 mx/x11/mx-window-x11.c | 30 +++++++++++++++++++++++-------
 1 file changed, 23 insertions(+), 7 deletions(-)

commit e99e596a50200967fd6700d8baf137a6fd281a4f
Author: Thomas Wood <thomas.wood@intel.com>
Date:   Wed Jan 26 11:28:32 2011 +0000

    item/list-view: Improve the freeze/thaw behaviour
    
    Use an internal flag to determine whether the view is frozen, rather than
    blocking the signal handlers. This means that if the list or item view is
    frozen and a model is set, the view will still remain frozen until thaw
    is called, even though new signal handlers have been connected.
    
    http://bugs.meego.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1195

 mx/mx-item-view.c | 38 +++++++++++---------------------------
 mx/mx-list-view.c | 34 +++++++++++-----------------------
 2 files changed, 22 insertions(+), 50 deletions(-)

