commit f88554e799b10a3165756246a04c98d3d63fa33d
Author: Thomas Wood <thomas.wood@intel.com>
Date:   Mon Jan 24 10:21:02 2011 +0000

    box-layout: store the 'from' actor when focus moves out of the widget
    
    Store the 'from' actor when focus moves out of the widget so that it can be
    used for the 'prior' focus hint when focus is returned to the widget.

 mx/mx-box-layout.c | 4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

commit 057384909ce3645ab0dc2c1d3e0921306f0a4186
Author: Thomas Wood <thomas.wood@intel.com>
Date:   Fri Jan 21 12:33:14 2011 +0000

    image: add a 'clear' function to replace the current image with a blank one
    
    mx_image_clear will replace the current image with a blank, transparent
    image. MxImage will also now be initialised with the blank texture so that
    the first cross fade will be between a transparent image and the new image,
    rather than cross fading with an invalid texture handle as the old image.

 mx/mx-image.c | 120 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++------------
 mx/mx-image.h |   2 +
 2 files changed, 98 insertions(+), 24 deletions(-)

commit b3ba0db4978a60114adec22d723f4ef4ba8334bb
Author: Thomas Wood <thomas.wood@intel.com>
Date:   Wed Jan 19 13:55:57 2011 +0000

    Fix a few compiler warnings when using more strict compiler options

 mx/mx-css.c      | 2 +-
 mx/mx-image.c    | 4 ++--
 mx/mx-slider.c   | 4 ++--
 mx/mx-stylable.c | 3 ++-
 4 files changed, 7 insertions(+), 6 deletions(-)

commit 7f61962da427567a5bf71c78ec803b4fc89a2b5e
Author: Thomas Wood <thomas.wood@intel.com>
Date:   Wed Jan 19 11:47:04 2011 +0000

    css: check more precisely for pseudo-class matches
    
    The pseudo-class list from the selector needs to be a subset of the
    pseudo-class list from the node for a correct match. The inclusion of an
    element in the list cannot be determined using strstr, since this may
    incorrectly match on an element that includes the string of another
    element.

 mx/mx-css.c | 87 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++---------------
 1 file changed, 66 insertions(+), 21 deletions(-)

commit 4271582fab95926a460dca821d3974e7944b3367
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Fri Jan 14 18:01:33 2011 +0000

    stylable: Add mx_stylable_style_pseudo_class_contains()
    
    Use whole-word matching to test if a pseudo-class list contains a particular
    pseudo-class and export this functionality as a public function,
    mx_stylable_style_pseudo_class_contains().

 docs/reference/libmx/mx-sections.txt |  1 +
