commit 63de940e85feab2c2adb8e8aa18489945afe8035
Author: Thomas Wood <thomas.wood@intel.com>
Date:   Fri Jan 14 15:31:56 2011 +0000

    css: add selector prioritisation by position in the stylesheet
    
    Allow two selectors with the same score to be additionally compared based
    on their relative position in the stylesheet, so that selectors that
    appear later in the stylesheet gain priority over those nearer the
    beginning.

