commit 2164699fac570b0f365a613f04bae59cbb248bb3
Author: Thomas Wood <thomas.wood@intel.com>
Date:   Tue Oct 19 15:30:10 2010 +0100

    css: support reading and matching multiple pseudo classes
    
    Read multiple pseudo-class values from CSS and concatenate them into a
    string separated by ':'.
    
    Ensure that all the pseudo classes defined in each selector match
    pseudo classes available in the node and increase the score by the number
    of pseudo classes that match.

