commit 94b4deb066ca6b6d3a8e68fd2f75a93e3caa9c44
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Wed Jan 12 11:54:58 2011 +0000

    window: Add functions for setting/getting window size
    
    Add new functions for setting/getting window size and fullscreen status.
    This works around the asynchronicity problems relating to setting
    ClutterStage fullscreen, and provides convenience for setting/getting the
    window size with relation to the window border.
    
    Works around http://bugzilla.clutter-project.org/show_bug.cgi?id=2496
    Fixes http://bugzilla.clutter-project.org/show_bug.cgi?id=2434

 docs/reference/libmx/mx-sections.txt |   4 +
 mx/mx-window.c                       | 177 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++----
 mx/mx-window.h                       |   8 ++
 mx/x11/mx-window-x11.c               |  10 +-
