commit 8ccf6e585edf523404532815d61d7c206fdea4bf
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Tue Jan 11 15:36:28 2011 +0000

    window/window-x11: Fix toggling the toolbar after mapping a window
    
    Previously, toggling the toolbar wouldn't reallocate the window contents
    and the X11 window backend wouldn't update the WM hints correctly if the
    window was already mapped.
    
    Should fix http://bugzilla.clutter-project.org/show_bug.cgi?id=2463

 mx/mx-window.c         |  2 ++
 mx/x11/mx-window-x11.c | 11 +++++++++++
 tests/test-window.c    | 29 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
