commit 612cca7492de9263b829ec142917fd9cf7a884c4
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Tue Jan 11 11:09:10 2011 +0000

    kinetic-scroll-view: Add an 'overshoot' property
    
    Add an 'overshoot' property that lets you define a resistance when
    scrolling past the boundaries of the adjustment, rather than disallowing
    the scroll-view to scroll past those boundaries. (off by default)
    
    Fixes http://bugzilla.clutter-project.org/show_bug.cgi?id=2507

