commit 216ee382448e33c47160d6fb64bebd83fae27a60
Author: Damien Lespiau <damien.lespiau@intel.com>
Date:   Mon Jan 10 10:22:14 2011 +0000

    shaders: Don't use a define private to Clutter
    
    HAVE_COGL_* are private defines from Clutter's config.h. COGL defines
    COGL_HAS_* symbols instead.

 mx/mx-dialog.c       | 2 +-
 tests/test-shaders.c | 2 +-
 2 files changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

commit 0169c50789e81716e4f9a4015645251d14f7ab1f
Author: Damien Lespiau <damien.lespiau@intel.com>
Date:   Sun Jan 9 21:39:35 2011 +0000

    shaders: Don't specify #version in 1.10 shaders
    
    By default the GLSL version of shaders is 1.10 (ie when not putting any
    '#version' in the source). Strict GLSL 1.10 compilers, say like Mesa <
    7.10 don't parse #version and then don't compile Mx shaders with this
    directive.

 mx/mx-dialog.c       | 1 -
 tests/test-shaders.c | 1 -
 2 files changed, 2 deletions(-)

