commit a6e304a284a0bd1a2d0a4ff3f6a2a5c78fb698cb
Author: Rob Bradford <rob@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Thu Jan 6 17:21:01 2011 +0000

    widget: Translate scriptable properties that are marked as MX_PARAM_TRANSLATEABLE
    
    Properties can now be marked with with the MX_PARAM_TRANSLATEABLE flag. If
    this flag is set then when the object is instantiated from the script any
    properties marked as such will have their values run through gettext to be
    translated.

 mx/mx-types.h  |  2 ++
 mx/mx-widget.c | 48 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++--
 2 files changed, 48 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

