commit 1f416fdd0523900055ca47fd78f1b43313c2fcee
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Fri Dec 10 16:56:34 2010 +0000

    icon: Add a new style property '-mx-icon-suffix' + bug-fixes
    
    Add a new style property, '-mx-icon-suffix', that allows you to style an
    extra suffix to append to the icon name. This is handy if you have multiple
    states of a single icon that depend on stylable states.
    
    This also fixes programmatically setting icon name/size not overriding
    the styled name/size, and the memory leak of the icon name on destruction.

 mx/mx-icon.c | 87 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-------
 1 file changed, 77 insertions(+), 10 deletions(-)

