commit b52c4cf5bd09c704adbab57b48fa1d05d78be46b
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Fri Nov 26 17:45:11 2010 +0000

    slider: Use key-press instead of key-release
    
    Use key-press instead of key-release and only swallow the event if we
    actually respond to the key event. This means we don't need to
    special-case left/right in the move_focus function.

