commit 04d5c59f0f68518e603e461e557a65173775e1c9
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Tue Nov 16 14:07:09 2010 +0000

    adjustment: Add a 'clamp-value' property
    
    Add a property that controls whether the value of the adjustment should be
    clamped to within its valid range (lower, upper - page-size).

 docs/reference/libmx/mx-sections.txt |  2 ++
 mx/mx-adjustment.c                   | 69 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++------
 mx/mx-adjustment.h                   |  4 +++
