commit 900d58421bc5f87f90a057b589a423133c38f497
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Tue Sep 21 13:08:35 2010 +0100

    dialog: Fix invisible dialogs when shaders aren't available
    
