commit d7aa690bc96903755e26d02d634baf79e001ce82
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Wed Sep 1 12:17:03 2010 +0100

    dialog: Respect window orientation
    
    Read and listen to the window orientation angle when parented to the stage,
    and apply the same transformation to the dialog contents. This allows a
    dialog to be parented to the stage and still respect window rotation.

 mx/mx-dialog.c | 48 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++--
