Date:   Fri Aug 27 09:40:00 2010 +0100

    window: Add an orientation property
    
    Add two properties to MxWindow, 'orientation' and
    'orientation-reversed', that allow the user to control the orientation
    of the window in 90 degree increments. Transitions between orientations
    are animated.

