commit 5bbb5586efa73a9cec3941bb24ff5568c9bec6cc
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Thu Aug 26 16:46:07 2010 +0100

    dialog / modal-frame: Merge MxDialog into MxModalFrame
    
    After discussions, it seemed that MxModalFrame was quite useless on its
    own, so this commit merges MxDialog and MxModalFrame, as well as fixing
    some interaction issues. MxDialog can now be used like a normal
    ClutterContainer and all padding/spacing is stylable.

