 mx/x11/mx-settings-x11.c | 36 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 36 insertions(+)

commit e3838a0d74570d02e20579b625a3f4cf780c3fa0
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Wed Aug 25 15:32:16 2010 +0100

    settings: Add MxSettingsProvider
    
    Similar to MxWindow, MxSettings is restored to its original class and
    settings can be overridden using MxSettingsProvider, which can optionally
    be implemented by a backend. MxSettingsProvider allows arbitrary
    overriding of getting/setting properties (per property) and allows for
    property change notification.

 mx/Makefile.am             |  10 +-
 mx/mx-private.h            |   8 ++
