commit b5a6ddbb3ed1a64695d31b5c09073e8f9a8284d0
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Sun Aug 15 11:25:45 2010 +0100

    window: Split window into a base class and a system implementation
    
    Split window into MxWindowBase and MxWindow, where MxWindow is the
    window-system specific implementation. Currently only implemented the x11
    window.
    
    Hopefully this is API/ABI compatible, it ought to be but I may have missed
    things.

 mx/Makefile.am         |    7 +-
 mx/mx-private.h        |    9 +-
 mx/mx-settings-base.h  |    5 +
 mx/mx-window-base.c    |  848 +++++++++++++++++++++++++
