commit dc876e96b864c2d71bc97f62631463aca9248ed3
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Thu Jul 29 10:34:04 2010 +0200

    finger-scroll: Remove MxFingerScrollMode
    
    Remove the scroll mode. Push-scrolling can be achieved by just setting
    a very high deceleration rate so there's no need to clutter the code with
    this.

