commit f09b246e80f15c48a80c7f59b797bfb8792a3a8b
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Fri Jul 9 18:38:14 2010 +0100

    modal-frame: Use the offscreen clone ability
    
    Instead of relying on a slightly hacky patch to Clutter, use MxOffscreen's
    new cloning ability to do the same thing. This now works fine with
    stock Clutter 1.2.

 mx/mx-modal-frame.c | 182 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++---------------------
 1 file changed, 109 insertions(+), 73 deletions(-)

commit da6122c67b3b368ae044c5c75f04509a64cf5f37
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Fri Jul 9 18:36:06 2010 +0100

    offscreen: Add the ability to clone
    
    Add the ability for MxOffscreen to be able to clone actors as well as
    act as an off-screen container. If mx_offscreen_set_child is called with
    a child that is already parented (or the stage), MxOffscreen will clone
    that actor instead.

 mx/mx-offscreen.c | 194 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++----------------
 1 file changed, 138 insertions(+), 56 deletions(-)

