commit 85afc2dc2b105cdcca7f8ce54033d68bed06697c
Author: Chris Lord <chris@linux.intel.com>
Date:   Wed Jul 7 13:26:06 2010 +0100

    modal-frame: New modal container widget
    
    MxModalFrame is a dialog-style widget that can be used to present an
    actor (such as a file-chooser) that you want to block the input of other
    actors. It low-lights and blurs the background and animates in the child
    actor.
    
    This depends on Clutter bug #2173,
    http://bugzilla.clutter-project.org/show_bug.cgi?id=2173

 data/style/default.css   |  10 +
 mx/Makefile.am           |   2 +
 mx/mx-modal-frame.c      | 608 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 mx/mx-modal-frame.h      |  82 +++++++
 mx/mx.h                  |   1 +
