Author: Thomas Wood <thomas.wood@intel.com>
Date:   Fri Feb 19 17:14:38 2010 +0000

    Ensure all non-standard CSS properties are prefixed with "-mx-"

 data/style/default.css | 10 +++++-----
 mx/mx-path-bar.c       |  4 ++--
 mx/mx-scroll-view.c    |  8 ++++----
