Date:   Thu Feb 4 14:47:35 2010 +0000

    [button] Don't chain up paint with content-image
    
    If the content-image property is set, only draw that and don't chain up
    in paint.

 mx/mx-button.c | 4 ++--
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

