Date:   Thu Feb 5 14:25:11 2009 +0000

    [build] Last fixes for out-of-tree builds
    
    In order to make objdir work we need to fix the inclusion path.

 nbtk/Makefile.am | 13 +++++++------
 1 file changed, 7 insertions(+), 6 deletions(-)

